timeline.summary: This document is a chain of custody record for evidence (EFTA00029899) related to a case (Case ID: 31E-MM-108062). The evidence consists of massage tables (one peach, one green), a collection of documents including thrift rental agreements, CDs, a guest house message book, and electronic equipment. The evidence was initially collected on August 28, 2006, from a location in Miami, Florida, and subsequently transferred through multiple individuals and offices (NY, MM, ECR8) with documented signatures and dates.  A significant portion of the record contains redactions, particularly on pages 2 and 3, likely due to sensitive information. The final chain of custody record details the relinquishment of custody to a law enforcement agency on December 26, 2025. The barcode associated with the evidence is E4229229.

This document is a chain of custody record for evidence (specifically, a box of documents and media) related to an unidentified case (identified by case ID 31E-MM-108062 and barcode E4229230). The evidence was collected on August 28, 2006, and initially held in NY - NEW YORK, subsequently transferred to Miami (MM - MIAMI).
